          "text": "<span class=\"codehilite\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"gt\">Traceback (most recent call last):</span>\n  File <span class=\"nb\">&quot;/tmp/marimo_1011626/__marimo__cell_rEll_.py&quot;</span>, line <span class=\"m\">1</span>, in <span class=\"n\">&lt;module&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"n\">parx_available</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n<span class=\"w\">       </span><span class=\"pm\">^^^^^^^^^^^^^^</span>\n<span class=\"gr\">NameError</span>: <span class=\"n\">name &#39;parx_available&#39; is not defined</span>\n</pre></div>\n</span>",
